{"tid":1616631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推翻獨裁暴政！700萬人站起來！","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:58:53.000Z","uid":137789,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"38bfb6e3761b710f3e4bc246afab8e7437c288c0","tid":1616631,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"點解仲諗一國兩制？<br />\n點解仲諗雙篩普選？<br />\n<br />\n唔撚獨立就返屋企啦！"},{"pid":"b374cc60d723e62381dd8f33721a28e76b3a7305","tid":1616631,"uid":249979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:30:39.000Z","msg":"首先要搞掂軍權，解散警隊"},{"pid":"9a82fc615be91b077964e595a7cd67a215f38ad0","tid":1616631,"uid":137789,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"而家咁嘅規模都唔提高目標，真係要為奴到2047？然後集中營？<br />\n<br />\n出嚟仲係屌警唱肥媽，五大訴求，六大訴求，十大訴求好未？有閪得傾？自治都冇呀！成日講違反基本法，基本法邊個有份，唔係我哋擁護嘅憲法，我哋要嘅係立我哋自己嘅憲法，而家嘅香港唔單止冇得你選立法會，連區議會呢個佢話只係咨詢架構嘅席位就唔撚俾選架喇，一個二個仲碌柒咁撚樣，勇武打生打死，坐十年，都冇意義，因為後面吶喊嘅只係五大訴求，只係死黑警，只係放人，到底大家知唔知自己需要嘅係咩？"},{"pid":"8e2cdc9143c719323b4cadd15b216b6002398301","tid":1616631,"uid":25573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"打得贏黑警再諗獨立啦<br />\n言之過早"},{"pid":"aab8b3067bda5d38a96a0ce07e2830cb933bcdd9","tid":1616631,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=6533e0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"